title: LURKY
deskripsi:
Black plastic ABS luggage featuring an embossed logo, a telescopic trolley, silent-run wheels, and an anti-theft slider zipper, along with a 3-digit barrel padlock. It comes with a 4-month limited warranty.
-20-inch luggage/baggage/suitcase.
-Dimensions: 49x35x23 (cm).
-Net weight: 2.8 kg.
-Maximum capacity: 40 liters/9 kg.
-Made of black ABS plastic 1.5 mm thick.
-3-step telescopic aluminum trolley handle with PVC plastic trolley handle cover.
-4 pieces of silent-run & 360-degree TPU PVC wheels.
-Anti-theft slider zipper with 3-digit combination barrel padlock.
-2-point flexible rubber-plastic handle.
-Black polyester inner sleeve with black screen printing.
-Black flexible strap inside.
-YKK(R) Coil Zipper inside.
Lock Instructions:
The lock is set at the factory to open at 000. You can keep it as your own combination or set a new one by following these steps:
1.Pull the little red button to set your personal dial combination.
2.Turn the dials to your personal combination.
3.Release the button and test the combination to ensure that it works properly.
To reset the combination, repeat the instructions using the last combination you made.
